// Phase 11 Browser FFI — real Teko source using @dom intrinsics, compiled by the
// `teko` binary to WASM. `@dom.method(...)` auto-declares a `dom.*` host import and
// lowers the call; string args cross as (ptr,len); the leading arg may be a nested
// `@dom` call. The auto-generated glue implements the imports; the host harness runs
// main() and checks the DOM.
@dom.setText(@dom.getElementById("out"), "hello from dom source");
